Record Class ModdedNetworkQueryComponent

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
net.neoforged.neoforge.network.payload.ModdedNetworkQueryComponent
Record Components:
id - The id of the component
version - The version of the component, if present

optional - Whether the component is optional
@Internal public record ModdedNetworkQueryComponent(ResourceLocation id, String version, Optional<PacketFlow> flow, boolean optional) extends Record
Represents a potential modded network component, used for querying the client for modded network components.
